						.name Мать Берёза
						.name-label (Это вы)
				.description
					.student-work
						img(src="http://gdj.gdj.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Mobile-Apps-UIUX-Design-1.jpg", alt="portfolio")
					p The point is that good design is a combination of the idea, and the implementation. They have to work together. There are many things that look good on paper, but are either very hard or impossible to implement in the real world, across a range  of devices, in a reasonably cost-effective way.
